main.slogan: New NFT trading card game coming soon!

hero.description_first: Become a Ranger in a new world. Join our Discord and Telegram for launch details.

one.description: Collect and grow rare animal cards, form your herds, fight with other players and sell your cards to other traders. Powered by Avalanche blockchain.

second.description: Wildalo is a wild world filled with amazing animals also known as wildlings . Wildalo players, aka Rangers, collect these wildlings to grow them (upgrade their levels), form herds with them and fight their herds with other herds to earn in game currency.
